goals.active: Find Wolf Havroun Solvi to close the Sons of Svanir portal.
goals.complete: Along with Eir and Garm, I defeated the Sons of Svanir. We couldn't save Wolf Havroun Solvi's life, but we did release his spirit and close the Sons of Svanir portal to the Mists. With order restored to the Spirit World and Valda assuming the role of Wolf Havroun, we're ready to meet whatever challenges lay ahead.
